Watch out!

244
00:20:10.622 --> 00:20:12.781
No wonder you mad.

245
00:20:25.968 --> 00:20:27.877
Don't worry. It's okay.

246
00:20:30.971 --> 00:20:33.130
You better get
the hell outta here.

247
00:20:42.064 --> 00:20:43.179
- Flip me!
- What?

248
00:20:43.315 --> 00:20:44.643
Flip me!

249
00:20:45.651 --> 00:20:46.564
Damn!

250
00:20:47.653 --> 00:20:49.443
Lee!

251
00:21:00.621 --> 00:21:02.328
No. no. no!

252
00:21:27.226 --> 00:21:28.304
Lee!

253
00:21:39.236 --> 00:21:41.808
YAU MA TEl POLICE STATION

254
00:21:42.196 --> 00:21:45.896
Look. you've been ordered
by the Ministry of Public Security...

255
00:21:46.032 --> 00:21:49.898
to assist the F.B.I. and Secret Service
in our investigation...

256
00:21:50.035 --> 00:21:52.324
to provide us
with whatever we need.

257
00:21:52.454 --> 00:21:55.988
You have information.
it belongs to us.

258
00:21:56.123 --> 00:21:57.998
This is still Hong Kong.

259
00:21:59.126 --> 00:22:02.660
Two Americans have been killed
on United States government property.

260
00:22:02.796 --> 00:22:04.670
Give me two copies of that.

261
00:22:04.798 --> 00:22:07.086
This is our investigation.

262
00:22:07.216 --> 00:22:10.252
Chief Inspector Lee
will supervise your people.

263
00:22:10.385 --> 00:22:12.591
No. he will report to me.

264
00:22:12.720 --> 00:22:14.961
Do we understand each other?

265
00:22:20.560 --> 00:22:22.682
What the hell is that?

266
00:22:22.811 --> 00:22:25.267
That is. uh...

267
00:22:25.398 --> 00:22:27.057
Chief Inspector Lee.

268
00:22:27.190 --> 00:22:29.645
I ain't never been humiliated
and embarrassed like that...

269
00:22:29.776 --> 00:22:31.650
in my whole entire life.

270
00:22:31.778 --> 00:22:35.276
Got me runnin' around Hong Kong
butt-naked. thanks to you.

271
00:22:35.405 --> 00:22:37.279
- Thanks to me?
- Yeah. thanks to you.

272
00:22:37.407 --> 00:22:39.482
You needed backup.
so I gave you backup.

273
00:22:39.617 --> 00:22:42.901
I was about to kick Ricky Tan's ass. and
his bodyguards'. till you messed it up.

274
00:22:43.036 --> 00:22:45.990
- Stop. I'm sick of your bullshit.
- I'm sick of you!

275
00:22:46.122 --> 00:22:48.529
I'm not the one runnin' up
in karaoke bars full of gangsters.

276
00:22:48.666 --> 00:22:51.702
And I'm not the one runnin' up in
massage parlors lookin' for crime lords.

277
00:22:51.835 --> 00:22:53.958
- It's my job.
- It's yourjob.

278
00:22:54.087 --> 00:22:56.624
You pitiful. man.
When are you gonna have some fun?

279
00:22:56.757 --> 00:22:59.673
When are you gonna take a day off?
When are you gonna go on a date?

280
00:22:59.800 --> 00:23:02.670
- I have plenty of dates.
- When's the last time you had a date?

281
00:23:02.802 --> 00:23:05.637
When's the last time you played
"hide the rainbow roll"?

282
00:23:05.763 --> 00:23:08.846
Huh? Let's hear it. Lee.
The Year of the Rat?

283
00:23:08.973 --> 00:23:10.931
You will never understand me.

284
00:23:11.059 --> 00:23:14.261
You right. 'cause I didn't even
understand what you just said to me.

285
00:23:20.608 --> 00:23:23.063
They got my passport
back at that massage parlor.

286
00:23:26.113 --> 00:23:27.821
Good afternoon. sir.

287
00:23:27.948 --> 00:23:29.489
- Lee?
- Yes. sir.

288
00:23:29.616 --> 00:23:33.482
This is Special Agent Sterling
from the United States Secret Service.

289
00:23:33.618 --> 00:23:35.491
Secret Service? Why?

290
00:23:35.620 --> 00:23:37.494
Have a seat. please.

291
00:23:38.789 --> 00:23:41.825
What I'm about to tell you
cannot leave this room.

292
00:23:41.958 --> 00:23:45.826
The men who were killed yesterday
were not American translators.

293
00:23:45.962 --> 00:23:48.452
They were undercover
United States Customs agents...

294
00:23:48.589 --> 00:23:50.629
trying to break
a Triad smuggling ring.

295
00:23:50.758 --> 00:23:52.631
- Smuggling what?
- We don't know.

296
00:23:52.759 --> 00:23:54.798
But whatever it is.
it got the agents killed.

297
00:23:57.513 --> 00:23:58.888
How can we help you?

298
00:23:59.014 --> 00:24:01.255
You can stay the hell
out of our way.

299
00:24:03.560 --> 00:24:07.259
- Thank you.
- I can get you Ricky Tan.

300
00:24:07.396 --> 00:24:09.685
No. We know all about Tan.

301
00:24:09.815 --> 00:24:12.021
That's why we're leaving
him out there as bait.

302
00:24:12.150 --> 00:24:14.901
This is a lot bigger
than Ricky Tan...

303
00:24:15.027 --> 00:24:17.600
and the Fu Cang Long Triads.

304
00:24:22.825 --> 00:24:24.449
Hey. cutie.

305
00:24:46.052 --> 00:24:47.961
Thank you. Lee.

306
00:25:17.494 --> 00:25:19.367
Carter! Carter!

307
00:25:21.246 --> 00:25:23.654
Heaven on Earth massage parlor?

308
00:25:25.500 --> 00:25:27.373
Heaven on Earth?

309
00:25:28.503 --> 00:25:30.625
Hello. Cheap suits.

310
00:25:30.755 --> 00:25:33.838
Hello. Cheap suits.
Cheap suits.

311
00:25:33.965 --> 00:25:36.172
- Cheap suits. Cheap suits.
- How cheap?

312
00:25:36.301 --> 00:25:39.005
- Cheap suits.
- Cheap as hell?

313
00:25:55.733 --> 00:25:57.441
Excuse me.

314
00:25:57.568 --> 00:26:00.852
Can you direct me to Heaven on Earth
massage parlor. please?

315
00:26:00.988 --> 00:26:03.739
- Hello. How are you?
- Okay.

316
00:26:05.491 --> 00:26:07.483
No. no.
Wait a minute.

317
00:26:07.617 --> 00:26:09.526
I don't want no chicken.

318
00:26:12.996 --> 00:26:15.997
I don't want no chicken!
What am I gonna do with a chicken?

319
00:26:17.083 --> 00:26:19.040
I don't like
my chickens live. okay?

320
00:26:19.168 --> 00:26:21.494
I like 'em dead and deep-fried.
You ever heard of Popeye's?

321
00:26:24.172 --> 00:26:27.172
No. no! No!
Don't kill chicken.

322
00:26:28.426 --> 00:26:29.706
Yes.

323
00:26:29.844 --> 00:26:31.883
I'm warning you.
I'm a police officer.

324
00:26:32.012 --> 00:26:34.384
Put the blade down
and let the bird go right now!

325
00:26:42.687 --> 00:26:44.560
You okay. Lee?

326
00:26:47.525 --> 00:26:49.896
All he wanted was some mu shu.

327
00:27:05.121 --> 00:27:06.070
Damn.

328
00:27:07.207 --> 00:27:09.993
Hey. taxi! Taxi!

329
00:27:13.295 --> 00:27:15.204
Follow that car.

330
00:27:16.715 --> 00:27:20.297
Follow that limo. This is a chase.
Wherever he goes. you go.

331
00:27:20.427 --> 00:27:23.925
You're not movin'!
This is the opposite of chasin'!

332
00:27:25.138 --> 00:27:28.221
What? I will slap you
if you don't move this car.

333
00:27:28.349 --> 00:27:31.135
I'm gonna slap you.
I'm gonna slap you.

334
00:27:31.267 --> 00:27:34.055
All right.
Okay. look. Here.

335
00:27:34.187 --> 00:27:36.096
You understand that?

336
00:27:39.900 --> 00:27:42.391
- Now you're speaking my language.
- Get the hell on then.

337
00:27:42.527 --> 00:27:44.566
Come on. let's go!

338
00:28:32.401 --> 00:28:37.773
We just heard Ricky Tan is throwing
a party on his boat tonight.

339
00:28:38.906 --> 00:28:40.151
Did you tell Sterling?

340
00:28:40.491 --> 00:28:44.321
Let him find out on his own. I want
the Hong Kong Police handling this.

341
00:29:12.683 --> 00:29:15.433
Wait right here.
I'll be right back.

342
00:29:15.560 --> 00:29:18.514
- You understand?
- Yes. I understand!

343
00:29:18.646 --> 00:29:20.804
And don't eat my chicken. okay?

344
00:29:22.399 --> 00:29:23.773
Jesus!

345
00:30:46.967 --> 00:30:48.342
How you doin'. baby?

346
00:30:48.468 --> 00:30:51.837
Carter. James Carter.
Baldwin Hills.

347
00:30:51.971 --> 00:30:54.047
Isabella Molina.
From San Juan.

348
00:30:54.181 --> 00:30:56.387
San Juan?
I know San Juan.

349
00:30:56.516 --> 00:30:59.516
I've traveled there many times
on my private plane.

350
00:30:59.643 --> 00:31:04.684
You must know my friend Pedro Morales
Magonzales Marato Molaso Mondustos.

351
00:31:04.814 --> 00:31:07.056
- I don't think so.
- You sure?

352
00:31:07.191 --> 00:31:09.895
Well. I'm sorry. I thought
you rode in the best circles.

353
00:31:10.026 --> 00:31:12.233
But listen.
Make yourself feel at home.

354
00:31:12.362 --> 00:31:16.441
You need anything... champagne.
caviar... my yacht is your yacht.

355
00:31:17.867 --> 00:31:19.242
This is your yacht?

356
00:31:19.368 --> 00:31:21.407
That's right.
I'm the owner.

357
00:31:21.536 --> 00:31:24.240
The captain.
El capitan.

358
00:31:24.372 --> 00:31:27.455
- El capitan?
- Yes. Listen.

359
00:31:27.582 --> 00:31:31.283
I'm not gonna play games with you.
I want you right now.

360
00:31:31.419 --> 00:31:34.253
I see me and you downstairs
in one of those bathrooms...

361
00:31:34.380 --> 00:31:36.253
in about five minutes.

362
00:31:36.381 --> 00:31:39.750
Well. I'm very tempted.
It's such a beautiful yacht.

363
00:31:41.969 --> 00:31:43.168
What's it called?

364
00:31:43.304 --> 00:31:46.388
- What's it called?
- Mm-hmm. Your yacht.

365
00:31:46.515 --> 00:31:50.558
- The S.S. Minnow Johnson.
- The S.S. Minnow Johnson?

366
00:31:50.684 --> 00:31:53.388
Funny. The name on the back
was The Red Dragon.

367
00:31:53.520 --> 00:31:55.311
The Red Dragon?
Are you sure?

368
00:31:55.438 --> 00:31:58.723
Oh. I'm sure.
Because this is my friend's yacht.

369
00:31:58.858 --> 00:32:00.980
- Your friend's yacht?
- And this is his party.

370
00:32:01.109 --> 00:32:04.810
I must've got on the wrong yacht.
All these yachts look alike these days.

371
00:32:04.946 --> 00:32:07.899
I knew somethin' was wrong
when my key didn't work.

372
00:32:09.366 --> 00:32:12.201
- Who's your friend?
- Somebody on the wrong yacht.

373
00:32:12.327 --> 00:32:15.162
Wait a second. I know you.
Steven Reign. right?

374
00:32:15.288 --> 00:32:18.453
You own half of Los Angeles.
What you doin' here in Hong Kong?

375
00:32:18.582 --> 00:32:20.787
I'm here for the weekend.
taking in the sights.

376
00:32:20.917 --> 00:32:24.001
You must have your own plane too.
It's fun. ain't it?

377
00:32:24.837 --> 00:32:26.710
- Shall we?
- Yes.

378
00:32:28.131 --> 00:32:30.420
Well. enjoy the party.
Mr. Carter.

379
00:32:30.550 --> 00:32:32.423
I plan to. Ms. Isabella.

380
00:32:32.552 --> 00:32:36.003
See you later. Stevie.
Be cool.

381
00:32:49.440 --> 00:32:52.524
- Ricky Tan. Where is he?
- I don't know!

382
00:32:52.651 --> 00:32:55.605
He killed a detective today.
Where is he?

383
00:32:55.737 --> 00:32:57.445
Who got killed. man?

384
00:32:58.364 --> 00:33:00.439
- Carter!
- Who died. Lee?

385
00:33:00.574 --> 00:33:02.531
- You!
- Detective Yu?

386
00:33:02.660 --> 00:33:04.533
- Not Yu. you!
- Who?

387
00:33:04.661 --> 00:33:06.036
- You!
- Who?

388
00:33:06.162 --> 00:33:09.993
Do you understand the words
that are coming out of my mouth?

389
00:33:10.123 --> 00:33:13.657
Don't nobody understand the words
that are comin' out of your mouth. man.

390
00:33:13.792 --> 00:33:16.331
Ricky Tan is waiting for you.

391
00:33:21.757 --> 00:33:24.130
What the hell
is going on here. Lee?

392
00:33:24.260 --> 00:33:26.797
Remember I told you
my father was a policeman?

393
00:33:26.928 --> 00:33:29.052
- Ricky Tan was his partner.
- What?

394
00:33:29.431 --> 00:33:31.507
Hu Li. you disappoint me.

395
00:33:32.767 --> 00:33:34.593
Have you forgotten where you're
from?

396
00:33:35.811 --> 00:33:37.719
Don't forget who you work for.

397
00:33:38.771 --> 00:33:41.391
You think you could ever be a
leader?

398
00:33:49.864 --> 00:33:52.271
Lee. I've been expecting you.

399
00:33:52.407 --> 00:33:54.399
Please ask your partner
to wait inside.

400
00:33:54.534 --> 00:33:57.072
- I ain't goin' nowhere.
- It's okay.

401
00:33:57.203 --> 00:33:59.824
- I'm not leavin' you alone.
- I'll be fine.

402
00:33:59.955 --> 00:34:01.947
- You sure?
- Yes.

403
00:34:03.374 --> 00:34:05.580
I'll be right upstairs.

404
00:34:08.420 --> 00:34:10.496
I know what everybody's saying.

405
00:34:10.630 --> 00:34:13.547
I did not blow up
the American embassy.

406
00:34:13.674 --> 00:34:15.584
I'm not that stupid.

407
00:34:16.885 --> 00:34:19.720
But I believe
some of my people did.

408
00:34:19.846 --> 00:34:23.428
My enemies
are trying to frame me.

409
00:34:23.558 --> 00:34:26.926
There is a war going on
right now within the Triads.

410
00:34:28.311 --> 00:34:30.220
I'm afraid I'm gonna
lose this time.

411
00:34:32.022 --> 00:34:34.727
If your father were still alive.
I would turn to him for advice.

412
00:34:34.858 --> 00:34:37.146
Please don't.

413
00:34:37.277 --> 00:34:40.479
Lee. I really need your help.
I cannot trust anybody else.

414
00:34:40.612 --> 00:34:43.234
Tell me why they killed
the customs agents.

415
00:34:43.365 --> 00:34:46.199
I'll give you all
the information you need...

416
00:34:46.325 --> 00:34:50.275
but you've gotta get me
out of Hong Kong right away.

417
00:35:32.612 --> 00:35:34.155
Lady. what are you doin'?

418
00:35:34.281 --> 00:35:36.653
Get down.
I'm L.A.P.D.

419
00:35:38.576 --> 00:35:42.075
You just kick me?
You must be outta your mind!

420
00:35:42.204 --> 00:35:45.537
You want some of me? I'm gonna
give you an L.A.P.D. Ass-kickin'!

421
00:36:11.811 --> 00:36:13.768
- You okay?
- Yeah.

422
00:36:13.896 --> 00:36:16.600
I slipped and I fell. Hey.

423
00:36:16.731 --> 00:36:18.688
- What?
- Am I bleedin'?

424
00:36:31.910 --> 00:36:34.615
Quite a night. Inspector.

425
00:36:34.746 --> 00:36:37.949
Ricky Tan was our only bait.
Now he's gone.

426
00:36:38.082 --> 00:36:42.458
So you got your revenge. at the expense
of a U.S. Government investigation.

427
00:36:42.585 --> 00:36:44.458
What are you talkin'
about. revenge?

428
00:36:44.587 --> 00:36:47.374
Now. I don't know if the Triads
paid you to get rid of Tan...

429
00:36:47.506 --> 00:36:49.831
or if it was a pure
vendetta killing...

430
00:36:49.966 --> 00:36:53.382
or if you're involved in the smuggling
yourself. but you're off this case.

431
00:36:53.511 --> 00:36:55.883
I don't ever wanna see you again.
Is that clear?

432
00:36:56.013 --> 00:36:58.847
- What's goin' on here?
- Carter. you're in enough trouble.

433
00:36:58.975 --> 00:37:01.725
Just shut up.
Stay out of it.

434
00:37:01.851 --> 00:37:03.890
You're goin' back to L.A.
Right now.

435
00:37:04.020 --> 00:37:07.719
That's fine with me. man.
I ain't had fun since I been out here.

436
00:37:11.483 --> 00:37:13.560
Sorry. Lee.

437
00:37:15.403 --> 00:37:17.063
Escort Detective Carter
to the airport.

438
00:37:19.491 --> 00:37:20.866
I'll take him.

439
00:37:20.992 --> 00:37:22.402
Get your hands off!

440
00:37:30.124 --> 00:37:34.167
- Carter. you don't understand.
- I understand. all right.

441
00:37:34.294 --> 00:37:36.665
I got knocked off a building.
I got beat on...

442
00:37:36.795 --> 00:37:40.460
I got stripped butt-naked.
and you held out on me. man.

443
00:37:40.591 --> 00:37:42.748
I'm outta here.

444
00:37:49.014 --> 00:37:52.098
Carter. Ricky Tan
set up my father.

445
00:37:53.643 --> 00:37:54.888
What?

446
00:38:00.064 --> 00:38:04.013
Five years ago. my father was working
a big international smuggling case.

447
00:38:04.150 --> 00:38:07.021
He found out his partner. Tan.
was working for the Triads.

448
00:38:07.153 --> 00:38:11.280
But before he could prove it.
he was killed.

449
00:38:11.407 --> 00:38:13.364
All the evidence disappeared...

450
00:38:13.492 --> 00:38:15.947
Tan resigned.
and the case was never solved.

451
00:38:17.996 --> 00:38:20.569
I get it now. This is all about
your daddy's last case.

452
00:38:26.043 --> 00:38:27.917
You gettin' on the plane
with me or not?

453
00:38:28.045 --> 00:38:29.243
What?

454
00:38:29.379 --> 00:38:32.084
You know my daddy
died on the job too.

455
00:38:32.215 --> 00:38:35.050
If I had a chance to square his death.
I'd do whatever it took.

456
00:38:35.176 --> 00:38:38.627
I'd do anything.
So you comin' or what?

457
00:38:44.684 --> 00:38:45.847
Why L.A.?

458
00:38:49.313 --> 00:38:52.645
Lee. let me introduce you to Carter's
theory of criminal investigation:

459
00:38:52.773 --> 00:38:54.646
Follow the rich white man.

460
00:38:54.775 --> 00:38:58.606
- Follow the rich white man?
- Exactly. Now you're learning.

461
00:38:58.737 --> 00:39:02.187
Every big crime has a rich white man
behind it waitin' for his cut.

462
00:39:02.322 --> 00:39:04.695
Now in our case.
we know who the rich white man is.

463
00:39:04.825 --> 00:39:06.698
- Steven Reign.
- Who?

464
00:39:06.827 --> 00:39:09.577
Steven Reign. the hotel billionaire.
I saw him on Ricky Tan's boat.

465
00:39:09.704 --> 00:39:12.076
When the shootin' started.
he was way too cool.

466
00:39:12.206 --> 00:39:14.697
When people start shootin'.
white people ain't that cool.

467
00:39:14.833 --> 00:39:17.121
They either runnin' around.
hidin' behind tables...

468
00:39:17.251 --> 00:39:20.287
or screamin' like. "aah!"

469
00:39:20.420 --> 00:39:21.997
You sound like that
all the time.

470
00:39:22.130 --> 00:39:24.087
Let me tell you somethin'
about black people.

471
00:39:24.216 --> 00:39:26.587
When stuff goes down.
we keep our cool.

472
00:39:26.717 --> 00:39:29.920
Maybe. but not like Asians.
We never panic.

473
00:39:30.053 --> 00:39:32.674
Right. When Godzilla's comin'.
y'all be trippin'.

474
00:39:32.806 --> 00:39:35.426
I seen the movie.
You be. "Gaica. gaica!"

475
00:39:35.558 --> 00:39:37.385
Yellin' everywhere.
I seen Chinamen...

476
00:39:37.518 --> 00:39:39.012
Mr. Carter. excuse me.

477
00:39:39.145 --> 00:39:41.386
Thank you so much.
It's the kosher meal?

478
00:39:41.521 --> 00:39:44.640
- Yes. that is our kosher meal.
- Shalom.

479
00:39:50.278 --> 00:39:52.603
REIGN TOWERS
Los Angeles

480
00:39:58.118 --> 00:40:00.822
There he is. right there.
Mr. Steven Reign...

481
00:40:00.953 --> 00:40:03.575
livin' large in one
of his penthouse suites.

482
00:40:05.582 --> 00:40:09.282
Oh. guess who this is.
Yep. that's her.

483
