01:17:53.768 --> 01:17:55.845
I enjoyed that little
story you told...

958
01:17:55.979 --> 01:17:58.435
about the dragon
and the treasure.

959
01:17:58.565 --> 01:18:01.187
My mother used to tell it
to me all the time.

960
01:18:02.903 --> 01:18:05.311
Do you know the moral
of that story?

961
01:18:05.448 --> 01:18:07.773
Greed will imprison us all.

962
01:18:12.121 --> 01:18:14.613
I hate that fortune-cookie shit.

963
01:18:29.181 --> 01:18:30.592
Just like your father.

964
01:18:32.810 --> 01:18:35.017
I really did try
to help him. you know.

965
01:18:35.146 --> 01:18:37.055
To share with him.

966
01:18:37.190 --> 01:18:39.681
To make your life better.

967
01:18:39.818 --> 01:18:41.976
But he was too weak.

968
01:18:42.112 --> 01:18:45.896
- Too afraid of change.
- Give me the plates.

969
01:18:46.033 --> 01:18:49.532
- It's over.
- I don't think it's over.

970
01:18:49.662 --> 01:18:53.446
There are casinos
all over this country.

971
01:18:53.583 --> 01:18:56.500
I can make you
a very rich man. Lee.

972
01:18:56.627 --> 01:18:59.035
Don't make the same mistake
your father did.

973
01:18:59.172 --> 01:19:03.549
If you reach for that gun.
I'll kill you.

974
01:19:03.677 --> 01:19:06.927
Don't you remember?
I'm already dead.

975
01:19:12.686 --> 01:19:14.264
Hey. Ricky.
How you doin'?

976
01:19:14.397 --> 01:19:16.639
Lee. I see you got
everything under control.

977
01:19:16.774 --> 01:19:19.775
I'm gonna go downstairs and...
Goddamn!

978
01:19:19.902 --> 01:19:23.521
- What happened to Reign?
- Shall I tell you how your father died?

979
01:19:23.656 --> 01:19:26.408
Hey. hey.
Wait one second. Lee.

980
01:19:26.535 --> 01:19:28.444
It ain't worth it. man.
He tryin' to trick you.

981
01:19:28.578 --> 01:19:31.200
- Don't go too far. now.
- He never begged for his life...

982
01:19:31.331 --> 01:19:33.573
- or tried to make a deal.
- Put the gun down.

983
01:19:33.709 --> 01:19:37.244
All he asked me. just seconds
before I pulled the trigger...

984
01:19:37.380 --> 01:19:40.167
was that I promise
not to kill you.

985
01:19:41.300 --> 01:19:43.459
Oh. he was so pathetic.

986
01:19:43.595 --> 01:19:47.213
Oh. hell. no. He went too far.
Shoot his ass right now. Lee!

987
01:19:47.349 --> 01:19:48.547
What are you gonna do?

988
01:19:48.683 --> 01:19:51.257
All you got to do is pull
that trigger back and bam!

989
01:19:51.395 --> 01:19:54.396
Are you going to spend the rest
of your life hiding like your father?

990
01:19:54.523 --> 01:19:57.096
Man. don't let him talk about
your daddy like that. Shoot him. Lee.

991
01:19:57.234 --> 01:19:59.560
- You can't do it. can you?
- Yes. hell. you can. Lee.

992
01:19:59.695 --> 01:20:02.317
- Ain't nobody up here but us.
- Just as I thought.

993
01:20:02.448 --> 01:20:04.073
He tryin' to punk you.
Shoot him!

994
01:20:04.200 --> 01:20:07.201
If you ain't gonna shoot him.
kung fu his ass or something.

995
01:20:29.060 --> 01:20:32.061
Damn!
Good kick. Lee.

996
01:20:32.188 --> 01:20:34.146
It was an accident.

997
01:20:34.274 --> 01:20:37.560
That's okay. We'll just say
he tried to catch a cab.

998
01:20:41.198 --> 01:20:43.321
What's that in your...
Oh. hell. no.

999
01:20:43.450 --> 01:20:45.906
Lady. you listen
to me right now.

1000
01:20:46.036 --> 01:20:48.954
- Put that bomb down and turn it off!
- Carter. we have to jump!

1001
01:20:49.081 --> 01:20:50.908
You crazy. I ain't jumpin'.

1002
01:20:51.876 --> 01:20:53.999
- Use your jacket!
- Hey. turn that bomb off!

1003
01:20:54.796 --> 01:20:57.121
Crazy-ass...

1004
01:21:11.314 --> 01:21:12.724
That wasn't so bad.

1005
01:21:50.439 --> 01:21:53.523
I cannot believe I flew
10.000 miles for this shit.

1006
01:22:05.538 --> 01:22:07.246
Detective Lee.
I hate to admit it...

1007
01:22:07.374 --> 01:22:10.873
but the United States Secret Service
is indebted to you.

1008
01:22:11.003 --> 01:22:13.161
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

1009
01:22:13.297 --> 01:22:15.171
I'll see you on board.

1010
01:22:18.010 --> 01:22:19.884
I want to thank you too.

1011
01:22:27.770 --> 01:22:30.606
It was nice working with you.

1012
01:22:41.327 --> 01:22:43.616
I saw that.

1013
01:22:43.746 --> 01:22:46.831
You sly devil. you.
She kissed you. didn't she?

1014
01:22:48.501 --> 01:22:51.253
You played it cool. too. walking away
and not looking back. I like that.

1015
01:22:51.379 --> 01:22:53.206
Yeah.
I'm a player.

1016
01:22:55.050 --> 01:22:57.719
- Where is she headed?
- She's going to New York.

1017
01:23:00.055 --> 01:23:03.887
- Is that your gate down there?
- Yep.

1018
01:23:04.018 --> 01:23:06.473
Well. I'm this way.

1019
01:23:06.604 --> 01:23:08.929
- Guess that means good-bye.
- I guess so.

1020
01:23:10.400 --> 01:23:12.273
Thank you. Carter.

1021
01:23:12.402 --> 01:23:14.441
Take good care
of yourself. Lee.

1022
01:23:18.742 --> 01:23:21.233
- Oh. Carter.
- Yeah. Lee?

1023
01:23:21.370 --> 01:23:23.528
What's up?

1024
01:23:24.623 --> 01:23:26.782
There is something
I want you to have.

1025
01:23:29.253 --> 01:23:31.827
No. This is your daddy's badge.
I can't take that. man. No way.

1026
01:23:31.964 --> 01:23:34.538
It's okay. No.
Finally. I can let it go.

1027
01:23:36.594 --> 01:23:38.468
Thank you. man.
Hey.

1028
01:23:38.596 --> 01:23:41.800
You know what?
I got something for you too.

1029
01:23:45.938 --> 01:23:48.690
I got it at the tables this morning
at Caesar's. I'm still hot.

1030
01:23:48.816 --> 01:23:52.267
- I can't take this.
- Don't worry. I got a lot more.

1031
01:23:52.403 --> 01:23:55.439
- Go ahead. Enjoy yourself.
- No. Carter. I can't have this.

1032
01:23:55.573 --> 01:23:57.981
Would you stop acting like a cop
for one second and live it up?

1033
01:23:58.117 --> 01:24:00.525
There got to be something
you want. Come on.

1034
01:24:00.662 --> 01:24:02.654
Think about it.

1035
01:24:02.789 --> 01:24:07.582
This is the final boarding call
for Flight 44 to La Guardia.

1036
01:24:07.711 --> 01:24:11.661
I always wanted to go to Madison
Square Garden. see the Knicks play.

1037
01:24:11.799 --> 01:24:13.957
- New York City?
- First class.

1038
01:24:14.093 --> 01:24:16.465
- The Plaza Hotel?
- Maybe a little mu shu?

1039
01:24:16.595 --> 01:24:19.217
- Amen to that. brother.
- So. what do you say?

1040
01:24:19.348 --> 01:24:22.136
You know what. man?
I can use another vacation.

1041
01:24:36.575 --> 01:24:38.235
- Action!
- Let's go!

1042
01:25:05.022 --> 01:25:07.062
- You all right?
- Is he okay?

1043
01:25:07.191 --> 01:25:10.726
- Jackie. you okay?
- Jackie always okay.

1044
01:25:10.862 --> 01:25:14.196
- Is this the kosher meal?
- Yes. sir. That's our kosher meal.

1045
01:25:14.324 --> 01:25:16.696
- What's the name of it?
- Gefilte.

1046
01:25:16.827 --> 01:25:19.448
- Gefilte fish.
- "Filk" fish.

1047
01:25:19.580 --> 01:25:22.332
Lox and bagels.
It's my favorite.

1048
01:25:22.458 --> 01:25:24.664
- What's the name of this stuff?
- Gefilte fish.

1049
01:25:26.379 --> 01:25:28.537
"Gefilke" fish...
What's the name of this fish?

1050
01:25:31.718 --> 01:25:34.125
You know what this is?
What is it?

1051
01:25:34.262 --> 01:25:36.587
- Gefilte fish.
- It's "filte" fish.

1052
01:25:36.723 --> 01:25:38.515
"Filte" fish. You want some
of my "filte" fish?

1053
01:25:38.642 --> 01:25:41.394
You want any of this...
What's the name of the fish?

1054
01:25:44.940 --> 01:25:46.482
Gefilte fish!
All right. Okay.

1055
01:25:46.609 --> 01:25:49.147
- Gefilte fish. I love this stuff.
- I really don't.

1056
01:25:49.278 --> 01:25:51.567
You have black people
all over the world eatin' this.

1057
01:25:51.697 --> 01:25:55.398
Who eats lox and bagels?
I'll have some "gilte" fish.

1058
01:26:09.425 --> 01:26:11.750
Lady!
Jackie. kick it.

1059
01:26:11.886 --> 01:26:14.211
Okay.
Chris Tucker!

1060
01:26:14.347 --> 01:26:18.096
- Jackie. kick it.
- Jackie again?

1061
01:26:18.226 --> 01:26:20.598
We'd love to see that.
Wouldn't we love to see that. Jackie?

1062
01:26:20.729 --> 01:26:23.350
Jackie. we'd like to see that.

1063
01:26:23.481 --> 01:26:25.558
Now. Jackie.
wouldn't we love to see that?

1064
01:26:25.692 --> 01:26:29.026
- His name is Lee. goddamn it.
- Lee. we would love to see that.

1065
01:26:29.154 --> 01:26:30.862
We would love to see that.
wouldn't we. Lee?

1066
01:26:30.990 --> 01:26:34.822
- There's gotta be something you want.
- I always want to go to Sw...

1067
01:26:34.952 --> 01:26:37.823
I always want to
go to Scra...

1068
01:26:37.955 --> 01:26:41.159
I always dreamed to
"Square Marden."

1069
01:26:41.292 --> 01:26:43.499
I always wanted to...

1070
01:26:45.964 --> 01:26:48.289
Now I'm gone.
Now I'm nervous.

1071
01:26:48.425 --> 01:26:51.960
Every "garden." I'm nervous.
Madison Square Garden.

1072
01:26:52.095 --> 01:26:54.302
I always wanted to go
to this Madison...

1073
01:26:56.642 --> 01:26:59.014
- There are a lot of men chasing us.
- As well there should be.

1074
01:26:59.145 --> 01:27:01.221
'Cause you're a very good-looking man.
If I didn't have a girlfriend...

1075
01:27:01.355 --> 01:27:03.229
I'd take a run at you.
put you in a bubble bath...

1076
01:27:03.358 --> 01:27:06.063
and put some water wings on you
and spank your little bottom.

1077
01:27:06.194 --> 01:27:09.397
But listen.
Here's what we do. guys. Easy. easy.

1078
01:27:09.531 --> 01:27:12.532
Look. you're giggling at me.
I'll take you home and just punish you.

1079
01:27:12.659 --> 01:27:14.735
I need both of you.

1080
01:27:14.870 --> 01:27:18.702
You sly devil. you.
She kissed you. didn't she?

1081
01:27:18.832 --> 01:27:20.872
- Yeah.
- I like that.

1082
01:27:21.001 --> 01:27:22.793
Oh. Hold on.

1083
01:27:22.920 --> 01:27:26.788
- Who's calling?
- Hello?

1084
01:27:26.924 --> 01:27:30.091
Hello?
I'm filming. man.

1085
01:27:30.220 --> 01:27:32.675
Call me back at 7:00.
I'm filming.

1086
01:27:32.806 --> 01:27:35.558
I'm looking Jackie Chan
dead in his eye. Call me back.

1087
01:27:35.684 --> 01:27:38.257
- Call me back.
- Are you a professional? We are filming.

1088
01:27:38.395 --> 01:27:41.978
- You turn on your phone?
- No. you can't speak to Jackie Chan.

1089
01:27:42.107 --> 01:27:44.100
No! They want to
speak to you. Jackie.

1090
01:27:44.235 --> 01:27:46.109
- Hello?
- I'm sorry about this.

1091
01:27:46.237 --> 01:27:48.906
We are filming right now!

1092
01:27:49.032 --> 01:27:52.615
You're sorry?
You wasted all our film!

1093
01:27:52.744 --> 01:27:54.902
Call me back later.
7:00.

1094
01:28:00.669 --> 01:28:03.836
Damn! He ain't
gonna be in Rush Hour 3.
